<h1 id="audio-commands">Audio commands</h1>
<h1 id="control-audio">Control Audio</h1>
<p>Plays, loops, or stops an audiosource. Any AudioSources with the same tag as the target Audio Source will automatically be stoped.</p>
<p>Defined in Fungus.ControlAudio</p>
