<td>Sound effect clip to play</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<h1 id="play-music">Play Music</h1>
<p>Plays looping game music. If any game music is already playing, it is stopped. Game music will continue playing across scene loads.</p>
<p>Defined in Fungus.PlayMusic</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Property</th>
<th>Type</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td>Music Clip</td>
<td>UnityEngine.AudioClip</td>
<td>Music sound clip to play</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>At Time</td>
<td>System.Single</td>
<td>Time to begin playing in seconds. If the audio file is compressed, the time index may be inaccurate.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Loop</td>
<td>System.Boolean</td>
<td>The music will start playing again at end.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Fade Duration</td>
<td>System.Single</td>
<td>Length of time to fade out previous playing music.</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<h1 id="play-random-sound">Play Random Sound</h1>
